- The most recent performance data implies the latest available year in the school_performance table.; 
- Average scores and spending ranges are aggregated metrics that provide insight into the academic and financial aspects of each school.; 
- School types and principal information add administrative context to the data.

sql:
SELECT st.type_name, st.description
FROM schools s
JOIN school_types st ON s.school_type = st.type_name;
